PNG2XYZ
=======

PNG2XYZ is a small tool to convert RPG Maker 2000 and 2003 XYZ image
file format into PNG images.

PNG2XYZ is part of the EasyRPG Project. More information is available
at the project website:

  https://easy-rpg.org/


Documentation
-------------

Documentation is available at the documentation wiki:

  https://easy-rpg.org/wiki/


Requirements
------------

libpng


Source code
-----------

PNG2XYZ development is hosted by GitHub.
Project files are available in Git repositories.

  https://github.com/EasyRPG/Tools


Building
--------

Run:

  make



License
-------

PNG2XYZ is free software. See the file COPYING for copying conditions.
